p: Table 1 lists some journal articles published from December 30, 2019 through February 23, 2020. These articles were selected based on collective use of factors such as journal impact factor, citation, and type of study. For example, the No. 8 article listed about the characterization of the SARS-CoV-2 genome has greatly facilitated the global effort to develop a vaccine for prevention of COVID-19. Also shown in this table are journal articles pertaining to potential antiviral drug candidates such as remdesivir, baricitinib, and chloroquine for the treatment of this disease.
